originalText.text:
We were fortunate to work closely with Douglas Kane on our build in Westport, CT. A renovation and new build, it was a large project that required new bathrooms, kitchen, and utilities.

From our first meeting, Douglas made every effort to understand not just what we wanted to achieve, but how we live our lives. His thoughtfully inventive and expert design maximized our space, incorporated special features like a music room and dog shower, and wove in existing furniture and pieces special to us. His incredible guidance and attention to detail is incomparable, and as a result our space feels elevated and unique to us. He also helped us source many beautiful materials from tile to antique doors.

Douglas also did an excellent job collaborating with our team of contractors and craftsmen, which was a great relief to us as we knew little bit about construction when we started the process. With Douglas’ help everything went smoothly and we felt supported at every step of the process. We couldn’t have asked for a better architect and will be forever grateful!
